**panel-checklist div 내부 (주석 대체):**
```html
<div class="panel-title t-purple">✅ 상한가 체크리스트</div>
<div style="display:flex;gap:4px;flex-shrink:0">
  <input id="cl-ticker" placeholder="종목코드 (예: 005930)" style="flex:1">
